#. <section class="sutta" id="an6.84"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an6.84:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 6"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 6"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an6.84:0.2"
msgid "8. Arahattavagga"
msgstr "8. Perfection"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an6.84:0.3"
msgid "84. Rattidivasasutta"
msgstr "84. Day and Night"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an6.84:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Chahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgatassa bhikkhuno yā ratti vā divaso vā "
"āgacchati hāniyeva pāṭikaṅkhā kusalesu dhammesu, no vuddhi."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, a mendicant with six qualities can expect decline, not growth, "
"in skillful qualities, whether by day or by night."

msgctxt "an6.84:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi chahi?"
msgstr "What six?"

msgctxt "an6.84:1.3"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu mahiccho hoti, vighātavā, asantuṭṭho, "
"itarītaracīvarapiṇḍapātasenāsanagilānappaccayabhesajjaparikkhārena, assaddho "
"hoti, dussīlo hoti, kusīto hoti, muṭṭhassati hoti, duppañño hoti."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant has many desires—they’re frustrated and not content "
"with any kind of robes, alms-food, lodgings, and medicines and supplies for "
"the sick. And they’re faithless, unethical, unmindful, and witless."

msgctxt "an6.84:1.4"
msgid ""
"Imehi kho, bhikkhave, chahi dhammehi samannāgatassa bhikkhuno yā ratti vā "
"divaso vā āgacchati hāniyeva pāṭikaṅkhā kusalesu dhammesu, no vuddhi."
msgstr ""
"A mendicant with these six qualities can expect decline, not growth, in "
"skillful qualities, whether by day or by night."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an6.84:2.1"
msgid ""
"Chahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgatassa bhikkhuno yā ratti vā divaso vā "
"āgacchati vuddhiyeva pāṭikaṅkhā kusalesu dhammesu, no parihāni."
msgstr ""
"A mendicant with six qualities can expect growth, not decline, in skillful "
"qualities, whether by day or by night."

msgctxt "an6.84:2.2"
msgid "Katamehi chahi?"
msgstr "What six?"

msgctxt "an6.84:2.3"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu na mahiccho hoti, avighātavā, santuṭṭho, "
"itarītaracīvarapiṇḍapātasenāsanagilānappaccayabhesajjaparikkhārena, saddho "
"hoti, sīlavā hoti, āraddhavīriyo hoti, satimā hoti, paññavā hoti."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant doesn’t have many desires—they’re not frustrated but "
"content with any kind of robes, alms-food, lodgings, and medicines and "
"supplies for the sick. And they’re faithful, ethical, mindful, and wise."

msgctxt "an6.84:2.4"
msgid ""
"Imehi kho, bhikkhave, chahi dhammehi samannāgatassa bhikkhuno yā ratti vā "
"divaso vā āgacchati vuddhiyeva pāṭikaṅkhā, kusalesu dhammesu no parihānī”ti."
msgstr ""
"A mendicant with these six qualities can expect growth, not decline, in "
"skillful qualities, whether by day or by night.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an6.84:2.5"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an6.84:2.6"
msgid "Arahattavaggo aṭṭhamo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pli3.435"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an6.84:3.1"
msgid "Dukkhaṃ arahattaṃ uttari ca,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an6.84:3.2"
msgid "Sukhaṃ adhigamena ca;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
#. VAR: Mahantattaṃ dvayaṃ niraye → mahattadvayaniraye (s1-3)
msgctxt "an6.84:3.3"
msgid "Mahantattaṃ dvayaṃ niraye,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an6.84:3.4"
msgid "Aggadhammañca rattiyoti."
msgstr ""
